videos.description: Ahmed Hill takes an early lead for the Hokies from deep.
videos.headline: VT's Hill knocks down three from NBA range

videos.description: Jordan Goodwin sees some space and knocks down a three to extend the lead for St. Louis.
videos.headline: SLU's Goodwin buries a three

videos.description: Javon Bess drives through the lane and gets the bucket to go with some contact.
videos.headline: SLU's Bess picks up the hoop with the harm

videos.description: Davell Roby keeps it going for Saint Louis behind the arc with a deep three.
videos.headline: SLU's Roby knocks down a three
